  "description": "A stunning nighttime view of a sprawling city illuminated with countless lights. The city extends along a coastline, with a large body of water reflecting the lights like a shimmering ribbon. A bridge or causeway is visible connecting sections of the city. In the foreground, dark silhouettes of trees frame the view, creating a sense of depth and perspective. Above the city, a bright moon dominates the sky, adding a touch of celestial beauty. The lights range in color from warm yellows and oranges to cool whites and blues, creating a vibrant and dynamic urban landscape. The scene evokes a sense of wonder and tranquility.",
